                    "value": "<p>The last guards unleash a soul-shaking bellow in unison. All creatures in a @Template[type:cone|distance:60] take @Damage[7d6[sonic]] damage (@Check[type:will|dc:42|basic:true]). Any creature that fails its save is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 3} (or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 4} on a critical failure).</p>\n<p>If the troop occupies 8 or fewer squares, this area decreases to a @Template[type:cone|distance:30].</p>"
