                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The last guards engage in a coordinated attack with their spectral curve blades against each enemy within 5 feet (@Check[type:reflex|dc:40|basic:true]). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d8+2)[slashing],1d8[void]]{1d8+2 slashing and 1d8 void damage}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d8+14)[slashing],2d8[void]]{2d8+14 slashing and 2d8 void damage}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(3d8+14)[slashing],3d8[void]]{3d8+14 slashing and 3d8 void damage}</p>"
