                "actions": {
                    "value": 3
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The last guards charge, swarming through their foes. The troop Flies up to double its Speed, dealing @Damage[4d8[void]] damage to each creature whose space it moves through (@Check[type:reflex|dc:40|basic:true]). Any creature that fails its save is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 1} (or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 2} on a critical failure). The troop can affect each creature only once in a single use of Spectral Charge.</p>"
